column1: Observed Geomagnetic Storm Parameters:Max Kp: 7.67Dst min. in nT: -223 Dst min. time: 2015-03-17T23:00Z  CME Note: This CME is connected to the long duration C9.1 flare with start at 01:15 and peak at 02:13, flare is centered in AR 2297, large part of the filament W of AR is also erupting, bright post-flare arcade later in AR 2297
